## Working agreements

All sessions on this repo follow `.claude/rules/working-agreements.md` — issue/PR/branch lifecycle, when to file vs not, scope discipline, lifecycle ownership. **Read it at session start before answering "what's next" or proposing work.** This is the durable contract for how we collaborate; the user drives product intent through conversation, Claude maintains the project board state automatically.

