## Keeping these files current

| When (concrete trigger) | What to update |
|---|---|
| Component moves from mock data → real API call | Status table in `<subdir>/CLAUDE.md` |
| A "Pending" row above ships | Move to "Done" in the snapshot table (Project is live source — table is just a hint) |
| Issue ships via PR | Close via `Closes #N` in PR body; if target ≠ default branch, also `gh issue close N` |
| New gotcha / constraint / decision found in a subdirectory | Append to that `<subdir>/CLAUDE.md` or relevant `.claude/rules/<topic>.md` |
| Stale fact found | Correct it in place — same commit as the rename if possible |

## Git

Always push immediately after each commit.
